thread.title: Darren Murphy (Myrtleford Rodeo)
thread.title_full: Ticketebo reviewed by Darren Murphy (Myrtleford Rodeo)

author: Darren Murphy (Myrtleford Rodeo)
title: Darren Murphy (Myrtleford Rodeo)
text: TIcketebo approached our committee online via our website of the opportunity and technology available for electronic ticketing for our rodeo. It was an offer too good to pass up and we had positive results in our first year and look forward to promoting this method of ticketing stronger for next years event.
